 * OneSignal local credentials template.
 *
 * HOW TO USE:
 *   cp config/onesignal.local.php.example config/onesignal.local.php
 *   # Then edit config/onesignal.local.php with your real credentials.
 *
 * WARNING: config/onesignal.local.php is listed in .gitignore and must
 *          NEVER be committed to version control.
 *
 * WHERE TO FIND THESE VALUES:
 *   - App ID:        OneSignal Dashboard → Your App → Settings → Keys & IDs
 *   - REST API Key:  OneSignal Dashboard → Your App → Settings → Keys & IDs
